verbose_text: Reductions of trehalase activity and trehalose level were found in Ab-tps1, Ab-tps2 and Ab-tps1+ Ab-tps2 RNAi treated A. besseyi and a significant reduction of trehalase activity and an increase of trehalose level were found in Ab-tre RNAi treated A. besseyi (XREF_FIG B), which indicated that RNAi was potent and specific for A. besseyi by soaking.
